## **Part 5: Migration & Deployment Strategy**

### **Deployment Order:**

```
Step 1: Deploy Support Contracts
â”œâ”€â”€ RONDilutionEngine.sol
â”œâ”€â”€ GroupCompositionValidator.sol
â””â”€â”€ GroupRewardDistributor.sol

Step 2: Deploy Group Manager
â””â”€â”€ RiddleGroupManager.sol (references support contracts)

Step 3: Upgrade Existing Contracts
â”œâ”€â”€ RiddleNFT.sol - Add group functions via proxy upgrade
â”œâ”€â”€ RONReputation.sol - Ensure compatibility with dilution engine
â””â”€â”€ RDLNToken.sol - Add burnFrom functionality if missing

Step 4: Configuration
â”œâ”€â”€ Link contracts together (set addresses)
â”œâ”€â”€ Grant permissions (group manager can call NFT functions)
â”œâ”€â”€ Set initial parameters (fees, limits, etc.)
â””â”€â”€ Test with small amounts before full deployment

Step 5: Gradual Rollout
â”œâ”€â”€ Week 1: Solo play only (existing functionality)
â”œâ”€â”€ Week 2: Enable group formation (no riddle attempts yet)
â”œâ”€â”€ Week 3: Enable group riddle attempts on low-tier only
â””â”€â”€ Week 4+: Full functionality across all tiers
```

