## **Part 6: Testing Checklist**

```
Critical Tests Before Mainnet:

RON Dilution:
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Single group: Full RON applied
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Multiple groups: Proper division (2 groups = 50% each)
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Max groups: Enforced correctly by tier
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Dilution updates when joining/leaving groups
â””â”€â”€ âœ“ Edge case: Leaving group mid-session (should fail)

Composition Validation:
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Rejects groups without tier diversity
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Rejects groups exceeding tier limits
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Accepts valid 3-member minimum group
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Accepts valid 11-member maximum group
â””â”€â”€ âœ“ Edge case: All oracle-tier members (should fail)

Reward Distribution:
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Correct RON-weighted calculations
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Enforces 70% maximum share
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Enforces 1% minimum share
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Sum equals exactly prize pool (no rounding errors)
â””â”€â”€ âœ“ Edge case: 1 RON vs 1M RON in group

Cost Collection:
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Minting costs split correctly
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Burn penalties split correctly
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Insufficient balance handled gracefully
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Partial failures don't corrupt state
â””â”€â”€ âœ“ Edge case: Member with 0 RDLN balance

Group Lifecycle:
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ FORMING â†’ RESERVED transition
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ RESERVED â†’ ACTIVE on session start
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ ACTIVE â†’ COMPLETED on finish
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Any state â†’ DISBANDED before riddle start
â””â”€â”€ âœ“ Edge case: Disband during ACTIVE (should fail)

Security Tests:
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Reentrancy protection on all fund transfers
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Access control: Only group members can submit answers
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Sybil resistance: Can't join same group twice
â”œâ”€â”€ âœ“ Overflow protection: Large RON values
â””â”€â”€ âœ“ Edge case: Malicious contract as member
```

